    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Architecture Diagrams"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mermaid diagrams allow you to create visualizations of complex systems directly in your documentation."
    },
    {
      "type": "mermaid",
      "diagram": "graph LR\n    A[User] -->|Navigates| B[Wiki Page]\n    B -->|Renders| C[Content Renderer]\n    C -->|Maps blocks| D[Block Components]\n    D -->|Displays| E[Browser]\n    B -->|Loads from| F[JSON Data]\n    F -->|Stored in| G[Data Directory]"
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "variant": "info",
      "text": "Mermaid diagrams are rendered client-side and support flowcharts, sequence diagrams, class diagrams, state diagrams, and more."
    }
  ],
